Ng3+ leads to a perpetual check.} (24. Kh1 Nxh5 $1 {Intending Ng3+ next.})
24... Bxd3 25. Kh1 $1 {The only move for White since 25.cxd3 Nxd3 is good for
Black.} Nxh5 $1 26. cxd3 Rxf1+ 27. Rxf1 Rxd2 28. Re1 Ng3+ 29. Kg1 Ne2+ $11 *


