-2]} 1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 e5 6. Nde2 {This move,
together with 6.Nf5, are the best options for White out of all these rare
alternatives. After 6.Ne2, White intends to bring the knight to g3 next.} (6.
