(13. Bc4 Nd5 14. O-O O-O $11) 13... Bxe3 14. fxe3 Nd5 15. Bc4 (15. Nxc6 Nxe3
16. Kd2 Nf5 17. Re1 Nd6 $132 {With the e and f-pawns, Black has good chances
