{Black develops with tempo.}) (11. Qd1 Bd6 $15) 11... Be7 12. Rd1 Qc7 $15 {
White's pieces are a bit awkward, especially the bishop on f1.}) 10... Be7 ({
It's not so clear after Black captures the pawn with:} 10... Bxc2 11. Qe2 Bg6
12. Qxe5+ Be7 {The engine assesses this position as equal, but it might be a
