18. Nxe7 Qxe7 $15) (12. c4 $6 Qa5+ 13. Kf1 fxe4 14. Bxe4 Rc8 15. cxb5 Nd4 $15)
(12. c3 Bg7 {Transposes to the previous lessons.}) 12... Bxd5 13. exd5 Ne7 14.
