16... O-O 17. Rae1 (17. f3 b4 $1 18. Nc4 bxc3 19. b3 Nxd5 20. Qxf5 Ne7 21. Qxe4
Ng6 $132 {[%csl Gc3]}) (17. Kh1 b4 18. cxb4 Rb8 $132 {[%cal Gb8b4]}) (17. Rad1
Rc8 $132 {[%cal Gc8c5]}) 17... Qc8 {The main move with multiple ideas: ...Nxd5,
... b4, ...Qc5. White has plenty of options, but we should not worry too much
