[%cal Ga3c2]} Re8 $5 (18... Qc5) 19. f3 Qc5+ 20. Kh1 e3 $132) 18... b4 (18...
Ng6 19. Bb1 Re8 {Also looks good.}) 19. cxb4 Bxb2 20. Re3 Bg7 $1 {Protecting
the king. Rh3 is met by ...h6 now.} 21. Bb3 a5 $5 (21... Rb8 22. Nc2 (22. Rh3
h6) 22... a5 $132) 22. g4 (22. bxa5 Rxa5 23. Nc2 Rc5 $132) (22. f3 Qa6 $5 23.
Rb1 Qb6 24. Nc4 Qxb4 25. fxe4 f4 26. Rh3 h6 27. a3 Qc5 28. Qf3 Ng6 $11 {
1/2 (42) Proof, M (2442) -Hensel, O (2385) ICCF email 2015}) 22... a4 (22...
fxg4 $5 23. Rxe4 Ng6 24. Rxg4 Qc3) 23. Bc4 fxg4 24. Rxe4 Ng6 25. Rxg4 Re8 26.
